% Source inspiration: surface cards in the official 2D PWR pin-cell example.
% Intentional simplification: original values and names; only one duplicated definition.
% Expected findings: SG001 ERROR for the repeated surface name fuelsurf.

surf fuelsurf cyl 0.0 0.0 0.40
surf fuelsurf cyl 0.0 0.0 0.41
surf outersurf sqc 0.0 0.0 0.65

cell fuelcell 0 fuel -fuelsurf
cell outsidecell 0 outside outersurf

mat fuel -10.0
